the point though -- we actually make a pretty good hunting pair.  Yes, the downtime sucks -- but I let him tank a bit, and start taunting off of him once he's used mend AND has taken some damage.  As a result, we generally end up down similarly.  We bandage to half (soon he'll be able to bandage higher than that! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  heal up a bit and he mends, and off we go again.  Life is best when we can get a healer to form a trio with us, but we're pretty effective anyway.  He can split pulls so we don't have to face swarms, he dishes out massive damage, he can feign the mob off on me if I can't taunt it off, and I can take the damage.  We have to pay attention to where we choose to fight, but it works.  We're both 41, and we've hunted together since 20, sometimes as a pair, sometimes with a cleric or a druid.</font><P>Loredena Frisealach Mainacier<BR>
Warrior of the White Wolf Clan <BR>
